#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.subtract.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.subtract"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:1 of
msgid "Subtract arguments, element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素相减。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:3
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:5 of
msgid "The tensors to be subtracted from each other."
msgstr "要相互减去的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，则其形状必须可广播到输入的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算通用函数，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:17 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- The difference of `x1` and `x2`, element-wise.  Returns a scalar"
" if both  `x1` and `x2` are scalars."
msgstr "**y** -- `x1` 和 `x2` 的逐元素差。如果 `x1` 和 `x2` 都是标量，则返回标量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:23 of
msgid "Equivalent to ``x1 - x2`` in terms of tensor broadcasting."
msgstr "在张量广播方面等价于 ``x1 - x2``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.subtract.subtract:26 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

